This paper proposes a novel technique for detecting adversarial samples in face recognition models. The technique is based on interpretability and involves identifying critical neurons for individual attributes and enhancing their activation values. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is computer vision (cs.CV), followed by machine learning (cs.LG) and cryptography and security (cs.CR). The paper also involves the use of neural networks (cs.NE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques.
